episodes.title: Hiraeth
episodes.plot: Frank wakes up after a month-long coma to find no one missed him. Debbie takes a criminal approach to making sure Franny grows up wealthy. Plus, Lip completes rehab and Carl, uncircumcised, looks into surgery.

episodes.title: Swipe, Fuck, Leave
episodes.plot: Frank starts a new life barricaded on the top floor of the Gallagher home. Fiona starts running Patsy's Pies on her own terms. Plus, Debbie gets into stroller trouble, Ian tries out heterosexuality, and Carl's forced into abstinence.

episodes.title: Home Sweet Homeless Shelter
episodes.plot: Kevin, Veronica, and Svetlana start a topless maid service. Frank makes new friends at the shelter to replace his old family. Plus, Debbie's lifestyle comes to an end, Carl gets a gonorrhea scare, and business at Patsy's hits the skids.

episodes.title: I Am A Storm
episodes.plot: Frank worries that he and his new family will lose their Home for the Homeless shelter, so he plans a little goodwill for the neighborhood. Meanwhile, Fiona drums up business by throwing a speakeasy party at Patsy's Pies.

episodes.title: Own Your Sh*t
episodes.plot: Frank learns that a billionaire philanthropist has bought the homeless shelter and he and his clan can stay. Meanwhile, Fiona gets smart financial advice from a Tinder hookup as Ian struggles with his feelings for Trevor.

episodes.title: The Defenestration of Frank
episodes.plot: Fiona sees opportunity in a laundromat for sale and decides to invest. Frank revels in the good fortune of his scam, but the troops catch a whiff of foul play. Meanwhile, Kev and V discover a shocking secret about Svetlana's father.

episodes.title: You'll Never Ever Get a Chicken in Your Whole Entire Life
episodes.plot: Fiona learns that owning a laundromat is costlier than expected. Frank helps Liam get into a plush new school after his old one is permanently shut down. Meanwhile, Debbie cleans up her act and grows closer to Neil.

episodes.title: You Sold Me the Laundromat, Remember?
episodes.plot: Fiona takes a DIY approach to renovating the laundromat. Lip agrees to go before the school board in hopes of getting reinstated. Meanwhile, Kev's trust in Svetlana wanes even further when the titty van goes missing.

episodes.title: Ouroboros
episodes.plot: Monica is back, and her first task is to help Debbie get back Franny. Meanwhile, Frank tries to avoid her, Ian has his first fight with Trevor, Lip tries to mask his relapsing alcoholism, and Fiona's laundromat gets a bad review.

episodes.title: Ride or Die
episodes.plot: Fiona, facing mounting issues, contemplates Margo's offer to buy the laundromat. Meanwhile, Ian tries to deal with the fact that Mickey might be out of prison, and Kev and V take matters into their own hands after Svetlana's betrayal.

episodes.title: Happily Ever After
episodes.plot: Frank and Monica have an interesting proposal for the kids. Lip buckles under pressure from Debbie to get his sobriety under control. Meanwhile, Fiona sees a business opportunity as Kev and V attempt to start a new chapter.

episodes.title: Requiem for a Slut
episodes.plot: The Gallaghers grapple with the loss of one of their own. As Lip takes steps to improve his future, Debbie, Carl, and Liam get roped into Frank's new scheme. Meanwhile, Kev and V get their revenge on Svetlana.
